jab bhi apki bigger problem ka solution depend karega choti and same type ki problem mai then waha recurssion lagega.

recurssion mai theen cheeze hai
1) Base case
2) Processing
3) Recurssion relation

Recursing ka ek recurssion call stack bhi banta hai.


Tail Recurssion mai sabse pehele base case hoga then processing then recurssive relation hoga.

Head Recurssion mai sabse pehele base case hoga then recurssive relation hoga then processing hogi.

Magical line - ek case tum solve kardo baki recurssion sambhal lega.


DP and recurssion ka famous pattern - Include or exclude patter.

Ek aur pattern hai jisme elements par for loop karke call marte hai.  
